(31, 1, '2014-11-03 08:40:05', '2014-11-03 08:40:05', 'McNally Sayaji Engineering Limited (MSEL), has been formed by the merger of Product Division of McNally Bharat Engineering Company Limited having factories at Kumardhubi, Asansol and Bangalore with the 60 year old Sayaji Iron &amp; Engineering Co. Ltd. of Baroda. MSEL is one of the country’s leading manufacturers of Crushing, Screening, Grinding, Material Handling &amp; other heavy equipment, serving the core sector industries.\r\n\r\nThe Product range includes Mobile Crushing &amp; Screening Plants, Skid Mounted Crushing Plants, Crushers, Screens, Grinding Mills, Feeders, Scrubbers, Stockyard equipment such as Stacker Reclaimers, Wagon Tipplers, Paddle Feeders. Open cast mining machinery such as Bucket Wheel Excavators, Shiftable Conveyors, Spreaders, Port Cranes. Mineral Processing plants such as Hydrocyclones, Flotation Cells, Thickeners, Slurry Pumps, Pressure Vessels, Heat Exchangers, Rotary Kilns, Driers, Coal Washeries etc. MSEL has recently also ventured into manufacturing critical fabricated equipment for nuclear power industry like Reactor Building Main Airlock doors. The Asansol &amp; Kumardhubi II units have been manufacturing critical equipment for the steel industry as per designs provided by International clients.\r\n\r\nMSEL has four manufacturing units located at Kumardhubi in Jharkand, Asansol in West Bengal, Bangalore &amp; Baroda. The manufacturing units have ISO 9001 - 2008 certification. In addition the Kumardhubi unit is certified for ISO 14001-2004. With Marketing &amp; Branch offices located at Kolkata, Baroda, Kumardhubi, Bangalore, Chennai, Secunderabad, Cochin, Nagpur, Vizag and Vijaywada, MSEL is geared to provide total customer support in any part of the country.\r\n\r\nMSEL has absorbed technology over the years through various strategic alliances and has established a strong R&amp;D and Design &amp; Development team to provide optimum and cost effective solutions to customer needs. The Department of Scientific &amp; Industrial Research (DSIR), a Government of India organization has given recognition to the In-house R&amp;D activities of MSEL.\r\n\r\nMSEL is a subsidiary of McNally Bharat Engineering Co. Ltd., one of the leading Engineering Companies in India having a Group turnover of around US $ 500 Million in 2012-13 and is a publicly listed company on the major stock exchanges of India. MBE has diversified interests in EPC business in Power &amp; Coal, Mining &amp; Metals, Steel, Port &amp; Shipyard, Cement, Oil &amp; Gas, Water and Infrastructure.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="leftcoll"><img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/themes/Mbe/images/collage.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="rightcoll"><a class="brochuicon" href="#">Click here for Brochures</a>\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<a class="videoicon" href="#">Click here for Corporate Video</a>\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-03 08:40:05', '2014-11-03 08:40:05', '', 7, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
