(67, 1, '2014-11-04 09:44:39', '2014-11-04 09:44:39', '<div class="con-block" style="text-align: justify;"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-206" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/asansol-unit-300x105.jpg" alt="asansol-unit" width="300" height="105" />The Asansol Unit is located at ADDA Industrial Complex near Kolkata and connected to the NH2 by a 20 mtr wide road. The total area is 25 acres (101,171 sq. mtr), of which covered area is 17,463sq. mtr. The covered area consists of 4 manufacturing bays, each 100 mtr long and 22 mtr wide with an overhead load carrying capacity of upto 100 MT and a hook height of 12 mtr and RCC trimix flooring for handling large loads.</div>\r\n<div class="con-block">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-209" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/doosan-cnc-machining-center.jpg" alt="doosan-cnc-machining-center" width="300" height="200" />The Asansol facility has several large machining centres like CNC Turning Centres, CNC Horizontal Boring Machines, Horizontal 5 axis Milling and Boring Machine (6 mtr by 2.6 mtr), Horizontal Floor Borer (2.5 mtr by 13 mtr), CNC Profile cutting machine and Submerged Arc Welding machine (Column and Boom & Trolley type), 4 roll Plate Bending Machine (upto 150 mm thickness, 3500 mm wide) besides other equipment required for large precision machining and fabrication.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Unit has manufactured various special purpose steel plant equipment and is approved by all the major European Engineering firms like SMS, Siemens, Danieli, Paul Wurth, Liebherr and Valmet (erstwhile Metso Power). It is ISO 9001 (2008) certified and approved by IBR and Nuclear Power Corporation. The Unit boasts of a highly trained and competent workforce and have undergone scrutiny of major European certifying agencies.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--1324" alt="" data-mce-placeholder="1" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Asansol', 'The Asansol Unit is located at ADDA Industrial Complex near Kolkata and connected to the NH2 by a 20 mtr wide road. The total area is 25 acres (101,171 sq. mtr), of which covered area is 17,463sq. mtr. The covered area consists of 4 manufacturing bays, each 100 mtr long and 22 mtr wide with an overhead load carrying capacity of upto 100 MT and a hook height of 12 mtr and RCC trimix flooring for handling large loads.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'asansol', '', '', '2015-06-23 02:33:18', '2015-06-23 02:33:18', '', 0, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/?post_type=manufacture&#038;p=67', 0, 'manufacture', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2014-11-04 07:45:39', '2014-11-04 07:45:39', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-191" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Bangalore-300x172.jpg" alt="Bangalore" width="300" height="172" />The Bengaluru unit is located at KIADB Industrial Area in Malur, 35 kms away from Bengaluru. Malur lies on the main rail line between Bengaluru and Chennai.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The unit is housed in a 16,000 sq mtrs plot and has a factory shed of 4,000 sq mtrs and a modern office block. The factory shed comprises of two bays of 20 mtrs width and 100 mtrs length with crane hook height of 12 mtrs and capacity of 20 MT. The factory has a fully equipped fabrication shop and a modern machine shop with CNC machines.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The product range at Bengaluru comprises of variety of process equipment largely catering to the mining & mineral, coal and power sector though some of the equipment do find applications in other sectors as in chemicals, glass, cement etc. The equipment range includes Slurry pumps, Thickeners & Clarifiers, Flotation cells, Filters, Centrifugal concentrator, Magnetic separator, fine screens, Conveyor pulleys and Pressure Vessels. Each product in the range reflects technology that is in line with the best in the world today.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The unit manufactures equipment of high quality standards and each product is fully assembled and tested before despatch.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--1197" alt="" data-mce-placeholder="1" /></p>', 'Bengaluru', 'The Bengaluru unit is located at KIADB Industrial Area in Malur, 35 kms away from Bengaluru. Malur lies on the main rail line between Bengaluru and Chennai. The unit is housed in a 16,000 sq mtrs plot and has a factory shed of 4,000 sq mtrs and a modern office block. The factory shed comprises of two bays of 20 mtrs width and 100 mtrs length with crane hook height of 12 mtrs and capacity of 20 MT. The factory has a fully equipped fabrication shop and a modern machine shop with CNC machines.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bangalore', '', '', '2015-06-23 02:34:57', '2015-06-23 02:34:57', '', 0, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/?post_type=manufacture&#038;p=68', 0, 'manufacture', '', 0);
