(195, 1, '2014-11-11 13:44:08', '2014-11-11 13:44:08', '<div class="con-block"><a href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/vadodara-unit.jpg"><img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/vadodara-unit-300x116.jpg" alt="vadodara-unit" width="300" height="116" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-192" /></a>\n\nThe Vadodara unit was set up in 1943 on 3.5 acres of land having a covered area of 12,000 sq. mtrs. It has a versatile manufacturing setup consisting of captive alloy steel & iron foundry, heavy machining, fabrication & assembly workshops. Over the years, it has developed a large base of quality conscious ancillary units. The Baroda unit has been awarded ISO 9001 - 2008 certification. The unit has a well-equipped design & engineering office and an R&D center. The unit had entered into a number of technical collaborations in the seventies for vibrating screens (Siebtechnik) and Crushers (Aubema). Although these collaborations have expired, the unit has absorbed the technology and gained technological expertise. In 2012, the plant has been shifted to Savli Industrial estate. The plot area is 26 acres. The covered area is 45,200 sq. mtrs. and the open area is 58,200 sq. mtrs.\n</div>\n<ul class="four-block-image">\n<li><a href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/fabrication-shop-vadodara.jpg"><img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/fabrication-shop-vadodara.jpg" alt="fabrication-shop_vadodara" width="300" height="200" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-194" /></a></li>\n\n<li><a href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/machine-shop.jpg"><img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/machine-shop.jpg" alt="machine-shop" width="300" height="200" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-193" /></a></li>\n<>', 'Vadodara', 'The Vadodara unit was set up in 1943 on 3.5 acres of land having a covered area of 12,000 sq. mtrs.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '70-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-11 13:44:08', '2014-11-11 13:44:08', '', 70, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/70-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
