(1349, 2, '2015-06-10 06:47:18', '2015-06-10 06:47:18', 'We at McNally Sayaji Engineering Limited, resolve that safety is an integral part of our Industry. We have adequate safety measures built in our plants, in Production &amp; Maintenance functions. Our endeavor will always be to keep the plant in the safest of conditions. We are committed to provide a safe, clean and healthy work environment to our employees, ensuring compliance with all statutory laws and regulations.\r\n\r\n<h3>We Shall:</h3>\r\n<ul class="list-arrow">\r\n	<li>Constitute a Safety Committee Comprising Management Staff and workmen for creating a total awareness about safety at all levels.</li>\r\n	<li>Operate with the conviction that all accidents are preventable and aim for "Zero" accident.</li>\r\n	<li>Impart training regarding safe work practices from time to time to one and all and keep them informed about safety advancement.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure that the Contractors, Transporters, other Agencies and Visitors to the factory abide by Safety Rules.</li>\r\n	<li>Provide personal protective equipment whenever and wherever required.</li>\r\n	<li>Encourage and create interest amongst all by organizing Safety Competitions, Slogans and Cartoon Contests.</li>\r\n	<li>Discharge our personal responsibility and cooperate and actively participate in maintaining and improving safety standards.</li>\r\n	<li>Follow safety rules, regulations, safe operating procedures / work methods that are designed to protect people and equipment from risk of injury or damage to property.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="center"><img class="bord" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/safety-training-in-progress1.jpg" alt="Safety training in progress" width="571" height="284" /></p>', 'Safety', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '160-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-10 06:47:18', '2015-06-10 06:47:18', '', 160, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/160-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(953, 2, '2015-05-18 08:08:33', '2015-05-18 08:08:33', '<h3>Celebrations galore</h3>\r\n24th Deepawali cum Motelian Nite was organized by Sports and Cultural Council of MSEL at our factory. The whole event created a festive environment in the organization and brought everybody together as one.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_265" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-265" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic6.jpg" alt="Lights and Festivities: 24th Deepawali cum Motelian Nite Celebration" width="300" height="200" /> Lights and Festivities: 24th Deepawali cum<br />Motelian Nite Celebration[/caption]</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_269" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-269" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic2.jpg" alt="The colorful and traditional Dandiya dance organized by Colony Ladies" width="300" height="200" /> The colorful and traditional Dandiya dance<br />organized by Colony Ladies[/caption]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Grand celebration on Republic Day &amp; Independence Day</h3>\r\nMSEL celebrated Republic Day &amp; Independence Day of our country in a grand manner charged with dignity, motivation and patriotism.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_268" align="alignleft" width="250"]<img class="size-full wp-image-268" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic3.jpg" alt="National Flag Hoisting on the occasion of Republic Day &amp; Independence Day" width="250" height="291" /> National Flag Hoisting on the occasion<br />of Republic Day &amp; Independence Day[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_267" align="alignleft" width="620"]<img class="size-full wp-image-267" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic16.jpg" alt="Annual Sports Meet organized by Ladies Wing at one of our factories for all the sports enthusiasts" width="620" height="208" /> Annual Sports Meet organized by Ladies Wing at one of our factories for all the sports enthusiasts[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Honouring the staff with Long Service Awards</h3>\r\nDistribution of long service awards by Mr. Subir Chaki, Wholetime Director was awarded to our workmen and management staff for their committed long association with our organization.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-266" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic5.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic5" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-265" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic6.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic6" width="300" height="200" />\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Fun and frolic on Annual Picnic by employees &amp; their family members</h3>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-264" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic7.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic7" width="620" height="244" />\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Zero Accident Awards for employees on 42nd National Safety Day</h3>\r\n42nd National Safety Day was celebrated at our factory. Contest was initiated amongst all workmen of the units, for drawing safety cartoons and safety slogans. All winners were recognized for their creative work, with some lucrative gifts. All the departments, who achieved zero accident during last year, were recognized with Zero Accident Award.\r\n\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-263" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic8.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic8" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_262" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-262" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic9.jpg" alt="A floral goodbye - Bidding farewell to employees" width="300" height="200" /> A floral goodbye - Bidding farewell to employees[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_261" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-261" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic10.jpg" alt="Grand Birthday celebrations of employees at office premises" width="300" height="200" /> Grand Birthday celebrations of employees<br />at office premises[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_260" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-260" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic11.jpg" alt="Celebrating the festival of lights with colorful Rangoli at Office" width="300" height="200" /> Celebrating the festival of lights<br />with colorful Rangoli at Office[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_259" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-259" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic12.jpg" alt="Traditional and festive mood - Celebrating Durga Puja/ Ayudha Puja at the Malur Factory" width="300" height="200" /> Traditional and festive mood - Celebrating Durga Puja/<br />Ayudha Puja at the Malur Factory[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_258" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-258" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic13.jpg" alt="Welcoming 2013 with cheer! New Year Celebrations at office" width="300" height="200" /> Welcoming 2013 with cheer!<br />New Year Celebrations at office[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_257" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-257" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic14.jpg" alt="Christmas spirit among the employees on the occasion of Merry Christmas" width="300" height="200" /> Christmas spirit among the employees on<br />the occasion of Merry Christmas[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<a href="#">All India Sales Meet and Product Application Programme at Kumardhubi</a>', 'Life at MSEL', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '173-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-18 08:08:33', '2015-05-18 08:08:33', '', 173, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/173-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1615, 2, '2015-07-09 06:04:35', '2015-07-09 06:04:35', 'Our Bengaluru unit has bagged a prestigious order for Iron Ore Beneficiation Plant package from M/s Rungta Sons Private Limited( RSPL) which includes  the total engineering and supply of key equipment up to product storage and tailing filtration. The unit also bagged package order for  three numbers of thickeners from Pacific Minerals, Jabalpur for their Iron Ore Beneficiation plant.', 'MSEL bags order for Iron Ore Beneficiation Plant package for RSPL, three numbers of thickeners from Pacific Minerals, Jabalpur and Dry Grinding Circuit for limestone from L&T.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'latest-news', '', '', '2015-07-10 05:47:30', '2015-07-10 05:47:30', '', 0, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/?post_type=news&#038;p=1615', 0, 'news', '', 0),
(1527, 2, '2015-06-23 00:40:47', '2015-06-23 00:40:47', 'MSEL manufacture cement plant equipment such as crushers, ball mills, material handling equipment, feeders, wagon tipplers, bucket wheel stacker cum Reclaimers. These are listed below-\r\n\r\n<a title="Jaw Crusher" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Jaw-Crusher.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Jaw Crushers</strong></a>\r\n\r\nThese are used as alternatives to Gyratory Crushers as primary crushers for crushing limestone when the throughput needed is less than 500-600 metric TPH. For hard ores Double Toggle Jaw Crushers and for softer ores Single Toggle Jaw Crushers are customary,\r\n\r\n<a title="Reversible Hammer Mill" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Reversible-Hammer-Mill.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Hammer Mills (Reversible Hammer Mill)</strong></a>\r\n\r\nReversible Hammer Mills, Open Bottom or With Grate bar type are used as secondary crushing of Limestone and Clinker.\r\n\r\n<a title="Heavy Duty Impactor" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Heavy-Duty-Impactor.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Heavy Duty Impactors</strong></a>\r\n\r\nFor higher capacities and crushing to (-) 20 mm, impactors are used for crushing Clinker.\r\n\r\n<strong>Bucket Elevators</strong>\r\n\r\nThese are used for vertical transport of powdery, small grained bulk materials e.g. raw meal, cement, bauxite, limestone, clinker, fly-ash etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Rotary Disc Feeders</strong>\r\n\r\nThese are continuous volumetric device reclaiming dry small lumps, coarse, fine grained and powdery material from surge bins and hoppers to feed subsequent equipment. In cement these can be used for dosing additives.\r\n\r\n<a title="Apron Feeder" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Apron-Feeder.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Apron Feeders</strong></a>\r\n\r\nThese are extensively used to reclaim ROM/ Large Size Limestone from Dump Hoppers for primary crushing.\r\n\r\n<strong>Conveyor Components</strong>\r\n\r\nMSEL product range includes all types of drive and non-drive pulleys, and idlers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Motorised Trippers</strong>\r\n\r\nBasically these are rail mounted conveyor discharging equipment to uniformly distribute the conveyed Ore over a large Bin or Ground Storage stockpile.\r\n\r\n<strong><a title="Rotary Scrubber" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Rotary-Scrubber.pdf" target="_blank">Drum Scrubbers</a> (Rotary Scrubber)</strong>\r\n\r\nThese are used to clean clayey/siliceous coatings from ore lumps as the first stage of raw material preparation.\r\n\r\n<a title="Circular Motion" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Circular-Motion.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Circular Motion Screen</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a title="Circular Motion" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Circular-Motion.pdf" target="_blank">Circular Motion Screens</a> are used to segregate various size fractions in ore streams. Sometimes used to reduce load on crushers by removing fraction which is already smaller than required size at other times these are used to recirculate oversize fractions from crushed product stream back to crushers. Possible application is in Mines before despatch to beneficiation plants as also in beneficiation plants. These Screens are available in 1, 2 and 3 decks to get 2, 3 and 4 size fractions respectively. Each size fraction may be requiring different post processing.\r\n\r\n<a title="Linear Motion Screen" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Linear-Motion-Screen1.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Linear Motion Screens</strong></a>\r\n\r\nLinear Motion Screens are used for similar applications but in more demanding situations, e.g.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Where the height is limited by surrounding facilities,</li>\r\n	<li>For the screening of small and short fractions</li>\r\n	<li>Where required throughput is high.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title="High Particle Acceleration HPA Screen" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/High-Particle-Acceleration-HPA-Screen.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>High Particle Acceleration Screens</strong></a>\r\n\r\nThese are ideally suited for screening applications for fine grain size materials (1 mm to 10 mm) with screening capacities up to 250 metric TPH. The base frame is agitated by means of eccentric shaft drive. The vibration is passed on to the dynamic frame via thrust rubbers.\r\nScreening mats between the inner and outer frame are clamped and flexed by the two vibrating frames. The relative movement of both screening frames creates a “trampoline effect” in the screen mats to create\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High acceleration up to 50g in screen mats.</li>\r\n	<li>Loosening-up and de-agglomeration of the product.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Grizzly Screens</strong>\r\n\r\nThese are used in primary crushing circuit as scalping screen downstream of the Primary Ore Crusher to separate undersized and oversized ore. Typical separation is at 80 mm. These are also used as Feeders to reclaim ore from Hoppers/Bins.\r\n\r\n<strong>Flotation Cells</strong>\r\n\r\nWe can offer Flotation cells for the lime ore Beneficiation or silica removal.\r\n\r\nSlurry Pump\r\n\r\nSlurry Pump for capacity of 2500M3/Hr is available in our regular product range for use in Lime ore beneficiation and silica removal.\r\n\r\nThickener\r\n\r\nFor the thickening of the limestone slurry/ tailing etc. we can offer proven thickening solution customised for the process requirement.\r\n\r\nLime Stone Beneficiation Plant\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>) We can offer the total limestone scrubbing plant with engineering for the small up gradation and removal of soil etc.</li>\r\n	<li>) For the Low grade lime stone we can give the flotation Plant with all the equipment and engineering.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'CEMENT', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '633-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-23 00:40:47', '2015-06-23 00:40:47', '', 633, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/633-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1506, 2, '2015-06-22 08:10:46', '2015-06-22 08:10:46', '<strong>Aggregate Production is consisting of following activities-</strong>\n\n<strong>Extraction</strong>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Stripping</p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Drilling &amp; Blasting</p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Shot Rock or Gravel Bank creation</p>\n<strong>Crushing</strong>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Scalping</p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Primary Crushing</p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Secondary &amp; tertiary crushing</p>\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Impact Crushing</p>\n<strong>Screening</strong>\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sizing &amp; Grading.</span>\n\n<strong>Sand Production</strong>\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Crushed sand of size 0-2.36 and 0-4.75 mm</span>\n\n<strong> Segregation</strong>\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"> Its screening process depends on products size</span>\n\n<strong> Stockpiling &amp; Handling</strong>\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"> Finished product stock of various size</span>\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"> Stocking bins of various size</span>\n\n<strong> Retrieval</strong>\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"> Final products of Aggregates of various sizes</span>\n\nFollowing MSEL equipment cater to above processes in <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><strong>Aggregate Production-</strong></em></span>\n\n<a title="Apron Feeder" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Apron-Feeder.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Apron Feeders</strong></a>\n\nThese are extensively used to reclaim ROM/ Large Size rocks from Dump Hoppers for primary crushing at quarry end Stone Handling.\n\n<a title="Jaw Crusher" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Jaw-Crusher.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Jaw Crushers</strong></a>\n\nThese are used as primary crushers in aggregate production. Either Single Toggle or Double Toggle Jaw Crushers are selected based on hardness and mineralogy of stones.\n\n<a title="Double Roll Crusher" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Double-Roll-Crusher.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Roll Crushers</strong></a>\n\nToothed Double roll crusher are used as secondary crushers in aggregate plants to crush (-) 25 mm size and smooth double roll crushers can be used for producing (-) 5 mm size of soft and medium soft rock.\n\n<strong>Cone Crushers &amp; VSI</strong>\n\nMSEL has agency agreements with reputed manufacturers to sell these equipment, which are required in secondary crushing to produce aggregate of size 0 – 40 mm and 0 - 63 mm (GSB) &amp; tertiary crushing (-30/ 10 mm) of stones for subsequent reduction to even smaller sizes.\n\n<strong>Bucket Elevators</strong>\n\nThese are used for vertical transport of powdery, small grained bulk materials e.g. raw meal, cement, sand, grits, Salt etc.\n\n<strong> Conveying system &amp; Conveyor Components</strong>\n\nMSEL product range includes all types of drive and non-drive pulleys, and idlers. Conveying systems are designed based on capacity, type of material &amp; stocking criteria\n\n<strong>Reciprocating Feeders</strong>\n\nThese are built for high capacity reclamation from surge bins, bunker and hoppers. A wide range of sizes is available in MSEL offerings. Heavy Duty versions with larger drives and heavier pans can be selected for coarse Stones and normal versions for fine Stones.\n\n<strong> Rotary Disc Feeders</strong>\n\nThese are continuous volumetric device reclaiming dry small lumps, coarse, fine grained and powdery material e.g. river bed gravel, sand, alumina etc. from surge bins and hoppers to feed subsequent equipment.\n\n<strong>Grizzly Screens/ Feeders</strong>\n\nThese are used in primary crusher operation in Quarry Mining as scalping screen downstream of the Primary Crusher to separate undersized and oversized Stone. This also separate fines/dust from the feed before crushing &amp; avoid contamination. Typical separation is at 80 mm. These are also used as Feeders to reclaim Stone from Hoppers/Bins.\n\n<a title="Circular Motion" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Circular-Motion.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Circular Motion Screens</strong></a>\n\nAlso known as CM Screens, these are used to segregate various size fractions in Stone streams. Sometimes used to reduce load on crushers by removing fraction which is already smaller than required size and at other times these are used to recirculate oversize fractions from crushed product stream back to the crusher. These Screens are available in 1, 2 and 3 decks to get 2, 3 and 4 size fractions respectively. Each size fraction may be requiring different post processing.\n\n<a title="Linear Motion Screen" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Linear-Motion-Screen1.pdf" target="_blank"><strong> Linear Motion Screens</strong></a>\n\n<a title="Linear Motion Screen" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Linear-Motion-Screen1.pdf" target="_blank"> Linear Motion Screens</a> are used for similar applications but in more demanding situations, e.g.-\n<ul>\n	<li>Where the height is limited by surrounding facilities,</li>\n	<li>For the screening of small and short fractions</li>\n	<li>Where required throughput is high.</li>\n</ul>\n<a title="High Particle Acceleration HPA Screen" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/High-Particle-Acceleration-HPA-Screen.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>High Particle Acceleration Screens</strong></a>\n\nThese are ideally suited for heavy and very heavy screening applications for fine grain size materials (3 mm to 10 mm) with screening capacities up to 250 metric TPH. The Inner frame is agitated by means of eccentric shaft drive. The vibration is passed on to the Outer frame via flexible thrust plates.\nScreening mats between the inner and outer frame are clamped and flexed by the two vibrating frames. The relative movement of both screening frames creates a “trampoline effect” in the screen mats to create-\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>High acceleration up to 50g in screen mats.</li>\n	<li>Loosening-up and de-agglomeration of the product.</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<strong>Banana Screens</strong>\n\nThese are multi-slope vibrating screens, come in single/ two deck configurations and are used in place of Circular Motion Screens when higher capacities (above 400 tph) are to be processed. The angle of deck decreases from feed end to discharge end.\n\n<a title="Mobile Crushing Screening Plant" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Mobile-Crushing-Screening-Plant.pdf" target="_blank"><strong> Mobile &amp; Semi-mobile Crushing &amp; Screening Plants</strong></a>\n\nMSEL has a large range of <a title="Skid Mounted Crushing Plant" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Skid-Mounted-Crushing-Plant1.pdf" target="_blank">skid mounted</a> and <a title="Skid Mounted Crushing Plant" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Skid-Mounted-Crushing-Plant1.pdf" target="_blank">wheel mounted Crushing &amp; Screening plants</a> in various configurations to suit multiplicity of sized products in various capacities catering to production of coarse, medium and fine aggregates and road stratum material.\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sand Plants</strong></span>\n\nMSEL Roll Crushers are suitable for making crushed sand. Roll crushers are suitable in secondary &amp; tertiary stage.\n\nFor <strong><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Infrastructure sector</span></em></strong> MSEL offers following equipment\n\n<a title="FB Series Dry Motar" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/FB-Series-Dry-Motar1.pdf" target="_blank"> <strong>Dry Mortar Mixing Plants</strong></a>\n\nMSEL-NFLG <a title="FB Series Dry Motar" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/FB-Series-Dry-Motar1.pdf" target="_blank">Dry Mortar Mixing</a> Plants are environment friendly and characterised by High Efficiency, Low Energy Consumption. The range Tower, Ladder and Station configurations covering a production range of 5 t/h to 80 t/h.\n\nFrom these plants basic grade and technical grade mortars are produced which are used as:\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Basic Grade</span> – Masonry mortar, wall render, base plaster, floor screed\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Technical grade</span> – Decorative plaster, tile adhesive, tile grout, water proofing, self levelling and thermal insulation\n\n<a title="Concrete Batching Plant" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Concrete-Batching-Plant1.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Concrete Batching Plants</strong></a>\n\nMSEL-NFLG <a title="Mobile Concrete Mixing Plant" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Mobile-Crushing-Screening-Plant.pdf" target="_blank">Concrete Batching</a> Plants are available in Station and Tower configurations covering production capacity range of 60 m3/h to 270 m3/h\n\n<a title="Asphalt Mixing Plant" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Asphalt-Mixing-Plant.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Asphalt Batching Plants</strong></a>\n\nOur offerings in this sector cover mobile plants of 90 to 120 t/h and stationery plants of 80 to 400 t/h production capacities. Asphalt recycling plants have capacities of 60-160 t/h.\n\n<a title="Mobile Concrete Mixing Plant" href="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Mobile-Concrete-Mixing-Plant.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>Mobile Concrete Batching Plants</strong></a>\n\nMSEL-NFLG mobile concrete mixing plants are available in 50, 75 and 100 m3/h capacities.\n\nSand Washing Plant:\nWe can offer the sand washing plant with the water recovery equipment for the best quality of sand production with conservation of environment. We can offer the customised solution for any size/ capacity as most of the equipment used in this plant ie Thickener, Slurry pump and Filtration System are our regular product.\nStone Cutting and Polishing Plant\nWe can give total solution for the slurry handling and ETP of the stone industry. We have the slurry pumps for the Grit recirculation, vertical slurry pumps for the water collection/ pumping, settlers, Flocculent dosing system and filter press under one roof.', 'AGGREGATE & INFRASTRUCTURE', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '635-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-06-22 08:10:46', '2015-06-22 08:10:46', '', 635, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/635-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
