w">\r\n	<li>Upgrade our technology to improve our products and services.</li>\r\n	<li>Educate and train our employees to enhance the quality of our products.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop vendor base, meeting ourdelivery and quality stipulations.</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce wastage &amp; non-value addedoperations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Subir Chaki,</strong> Wholetime Director</p>', 'Quality Overview', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-19 00:04:29', '2015-05-19 00:04:29', '', 154, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(972, 2, '2015-06-23 01:52:14', '2015-06-23 01:52:14', '<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>ZHENGZHOU YIFAN MACHINERY CO., LTD.</strong></span>\n\nZhengzhou Yifan Machinery Co., Ltd is a reputed manufacturer of various types of crushing equipment including jaw, cone and VSI, both for stationary and mobile plants. It has several installations within China and around the world.\n\nMcNally Sayaji has entered into a strategic alliance with Yifan for complementing the range of crushers to cater to emerging demands of the Indian market in the aggregate sector. With this alliance in place, McNally Sayaji has been successfully offer and bag orders for the mobile crushing and screening plants ranging from 100 TPH to 250 TPH.\n\n<img class="alignleft wp-image-1536" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/yifan-Factory.png" alt="yifan- Factory" width="550" height="374" />\n<img class="alignleft wp-image-1537 size-full" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Yifan-factory2.png" alt="Yifan- factory2" width="596" height="308" />\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>FUJIAN SOUTH HIGHWAY MACHINERY CO. LTD.</strong></span>\n\nFujian South Highway Machinery Co. Ltd., situated in the Southern Province of Fujian, is a 20 year old leading construction equipment manufacturing company in China and has several installations all over the world, namely Russia, Europe, Asia, Middle East, Africa, South America in addition to over 4000 installations in the domestic Chinese market.\n\nMcNally Sayaji has formed a Joint Venture with NFLG by the name McNally Sayaji NFLG Construction Equipment Co. Pvt. Ltd for manufacture and sale of asphalt and concrete batching plants, both mobile and stationary and dry mortar mixing plant. The asphalt batching plant size ranges from 80 to 400 MT/hr. The concrete batching plant capacity ranges from 60 cu mtr/hr to 225 cu mtr/hr. The dry mortar mixing plant capacity is 10 MT/hr to 80 MT/hr.\n\nAll the equipment are being manufactured at McNally Sayaji factories with NFLG designs suitably adapted, with special features over other existing competition products to the exacting needs of the well informed and demanding Indian customer. Backed by our competent service team at strategic locations all over India, we believe that we can make a difference to our esteemed customer’s business.\n\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1367" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/NFLG.jpg" alt="NFLG" width="100%" height="400" />', 'Associates', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '970-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-06-23 01:52:14', '2015-06-23 01:52:14', '', 970, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/970-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
