 shall –</strong>\r\n<ul class="list-arrow">\r\n	<li>Upgrade our technology to improve our products and services.</li>\r\n	<li>Educate and train our employees to enhance the quality of our products.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop vendor base, meeting ourdelivery and quality stipulations.</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce wastage &amp; non-value addedoperations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Subir Chaki,</strong> Wholetime Director</p>', 'Quality Overview', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-21 12:24:31', '2015-05-21 12:24:31', '', 154, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
